The '''Chad Cultural Centre''' is an institution located in [[Mao, Chad|Mao]], [[Chad]].<ref>[http://www.travelBlog.org/Photos/30887 The Cultural Centre Moa, Chad] in [[TravelBlog.org]]</ref>  It was founded by the government in order to foster national traditions.<ref>[http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-54939/Chad Chad: Cultural life] in [[Encyclopædia Britannica]]</ref>

